vernac_cmds: Variable K_eq_dec : forall k k' : K, {k = k'} + {k <> k'}.
Fixpoint assoc (l : list (K * V)) (k : K) : option V := match l with | [] => None | (k', v) :: l' => if K_eq_dec k k' then Some v else assoc l' k end.
Definition assoc_default (l : list (K * V)) (k : K) (default : V) : V := match (assoc l k) with | Some x => x | None => default end.
Fixpoint assoc_set (l : list (K * V)) (k : K) (v : V) : list (K * V) := match l with | [] => [(k, v)] | (k', v') :: l' => if K_eq_dec k k' then (k, v) :: l' else (k', v') :: (assoc_set l' k v) end.
Fixpoint assoc_del (l : list (K * V)) (k : K) : list (K * V) := match l with | [] => [] | (k', v') :: l' => if K_eq_dec k k' then assoc_del l' k else (k', v') :: (assoc_del l' k) end.
Lemma get_set_same : forall k v l, assoc (assoc_set l k v) k = Some v.
induction l; intros; simpl; repeat (break_match; simpl); subst; congruence.
Lemma get_set_same' : forall k k' v l, k = k' -> assoc (assoc_set l k v) k' = Some v.
Lemma get_set_diff : forall k k' v l, k <> k' -> assoc (assoc_set l k v) k' = assoc l k'.
induction l; intros; simpl; repeat (break_match; simpl); subst; try congruence; auto.
Lemma not_in_assoc : forall k l, ~ In k (map (@fst _ _) l) -> assoc l k = None.
Lemma get_del_same : forall k l, assoc (assoc_del l k) k = None.
repeat break_match; subst; simpl in *; auto.
Lemma get_del_diff : forall k k' l, k <> k' -> assoc (assoc_del l k') k = assoc l k.
repeat (break_match; simpl); subst; try congruence; auto.
Lemma get_set_diff_default : forall (k k' : K) (v : V) l d, k <> k' -> assoc_default (assoc_set l k v) k' d = assoc_default l k' d.
repeat break_match; auto; rewrite get_set_diff in * by auto; congruence.
Lemma get_set_same_default : forall (k : K) (v : V) l d, assoc_default (assoc_set l k v) k d = v.
repeat break_match; auto; rewrite get_set_same in *; congruence.
Lemma assoc_assoc_default: forall l k (v : V) d, assoc l k = Some v -> assoc_default l k d = v.
Lemma assoc_assoc_default_missing: forall (l : list (K * V)) k d, assoc l k = None -> assoc_default l k d = d.
Lemma assoc_set_same : forall (l : list (K * V)) k v, assoc l k = Some v -> assoc_set l k v = l.
induction l; simpl in *; auto; try congruence.
Lemma assoc_default_assoc_set : forall l (k : K) (v : V) d, assoc_default (assoc_set l k v) k d = v.
Lemma assoc_set_assoc_set_same : forall l (k : K) (v : V) v', assoc_set (assoc_set l k v) k v' = assoc_set l k v'.
induction l; intros; simpl in *; repeat break_match; simpl in *; subst; try congruence; eauto; break_if; congruence.
Definition a_equiv (l1 : list (K * V)) l2 := forall k, assoc l1 k = assoc l2 k.
Lemma a_equiv_refl : forall l, a_equiv l l.
Lemma a_equiv_sym : forall l l', a_equiv l l' -> a_equiv l' l.
Lemma a_equiv_trans : forall l l' l'', a_equiv l l' -> a_equiv l' l'' -> a_equiv l l''.

Ltac assoc_destruct := match goal with | [ |- context [assoc (assoc_set _ ?k0' _) ?k0 ] ] => destruct (K_eq_dec k0 k0'); [subst k0'; rewrite get_set_same with (k := k0)| rewrite get_set_diff with (k' := k0) by auto] end.
Ltac assoc_rewrite := match goal with | [ |- context [assoc (assoc_set _ ?k0' _) ?k0 ] ] => first [rewrite get_set_same with (k := k0) by auto | rewrite get_set_diff with (k' := k0) by auto ] end.
Lemma assoc_set_assoc_set_diff : forall l (k : K) (v : V) k' v', k <> k' -> a_equiv (assoc_set (assoc_set l k v) k' v') (assoc_set (assoc_set l k' v') k v).
Lemma a_equiv_nil : forall l, a_equiv l [] -> l = [].
Lemma assoc_set_a_equiv : forall l l' (k : K) (v : V), a_equiv l l' -> a_equiv (assoc_set l k v) (assoc_set l' k v).
Lemma assoc_default_a_equiv : forall l l' (k : K) (v : V), a_equiv l l' -> assoc_default l k v = assoc_default l' k v.
Lemma assoc_a_equiv : forall l l' (k : K), a_equiv l l' -> assoc l k = assoc l' k.
Lemma assoc_default_assoc_set_diff : forall (l : list (K * V)) k v k' d, k <> k' -> assoc_default (assoc_set l k' v) k d = assoc_default l k d.

command: induction l; intros; simpl; repeat (break_match; simpl); subst; congruence.
induction l; intros; simpl; repeat (break_match; simpl); subst; try congruence; auto.
repeat break_match; subst; simpl in *; auto.
repeat (break_match; simpl); subst; try congruence; auto.
repeat break_match; auto; rewrite get_set_diff in * by auto; congruence.
repeat break_match; auto; rewrite get_set_same in *; congruence.
induction l; simpl in *; auto; try congruence.
induction l; intros; simpl in *; repeat break_match; simpl in *; subst; try congruence; eauto; break_if; congruence.
